    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it shows! It\u2019s in absolutely pristine shape, inside and out, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
